01:12.053 --> 01:36.728
use them but they're not for circulation you can look at them there you can't I guess so and I guess decisions are made in an individual basis whether or not we will allow photocopies you might want to talk with him he's in the Grolier Club book there's only two N's in his tannin bound it's not the usual 3N tannin bound he's a 2N tannin bound you might want to talk to him about that he's got a nifty idea and

